name: Just Arrived
description:
Traveling far from home, bringing Rai & Raka to a city they have never been to. Their first goal is to find a house (boarding house) to live in while in this new city.

This is the beginning of their adventure in their new city.

They both found a baseball bat on the way and brought it first to make sure it could one day meet its owner and then be given to him.
The baseball bat reads "property of NIIX".

Raka tried to find the location of the house through the map he brought, while his older brother Rai was so tired of waiting for his younger brother.

what do they do next to find a new home in their new city, see you in episode 2 of the series " New Friend, New Home ".
